high_descs: Turn around and go near the diningtable.
Take the book from the table.
Turn around and go near the cabinet.
Put the book on the cabinet.
Turn around and go to the desk in the bedroom.
Take another book from the table.
Turn around and go near the cabinet on the next room.
Put the book on the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Collect the book and placed it into the cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left go to the hall beside the TV, turn left into the first room on the left, go to the diningtable in the corner.
Pick up the book on the table.
Turn around to the tall cabinet across from the table.
Place the book in the tall cabinet.
Go to the door and turn left, then turn left in to the left room, go to the desk behind the green chair.
Pick up the book on the desk.
Turn right at the door go to the next room on the right, go across to the tall cabinet across from the table.
Place the book in the tall cabinet to the right of the other book.
anns.task_desc: Place two books in a tall cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and go straight a bit, then right into the hallway, and take the first left into the room with the white diningtable.
Pick up the book from the table.
Turn around to the cabinet behind you.
Put the book in the cabinet.
Exit the room the way you came in, turn left and go straight until the last door on the left, going to the desk next to the entrance.
Pick up the book from the desk.
Return to the cabinet.
Place the second book in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place two books in the cabinet.
